data.description: Welcome home!  This three story townhome features a first floor den, two car garage, open concept kitchen and living room and a large primary bedroom.  Your kitchen will have stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops and LVP flooring throughout. The home also has a tankless water heater and the washer and dryer do convey with the home.  The neighborhood features a wonderful swimming pool and club house for all your party needs. Don't want a lawn to mow? Ready for a move in ready home?  Then this is the home for you.
